Angeles police officer last year. JIM MENDENHALL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Burnis White, an instructor at the Police Academy, demonstrates pain-compliance 
techniques that the department currently uses to gain cooperation of arrestees. 
PATRICK DOWNS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
