LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; LOS ANGELES POLICE DEPARTMENT; MARTIAL ARTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010890-0032 </DOCNO>
