-- ECONOMY; USSR -- POLITICS; NATIONALISM; COMMUNIST PARTY (USSR); LITHUANIA -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; USSR -- TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
