TRAFFIC VIOLATIONS; SURVEILLANCE; DETECTION DEVICES; CALIFORNIA HIGHWAY PATROL; 
CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION; LAW ENFORCEMENT; POLICE EQUIPMENT 
</P>
