SAN DIEGO POLICE DEPARTMENT; MARTIAL ARTS; POLICE EQUIPMENT; WEAPONS; 
DEMONSTRATIONS -- SAN DIEGO; POLICE BRUTALITY; CIVIL DISOBEDIENCE; ABORTION; 
OPERATION RESCUE; PAIN; LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; POLICE -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010890-0066 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 159172 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 8, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
